lead_paragraph: Ireland and Wales emerged relatively unscathed from a bruising battle in Dublin, although Ireland’s Keith Earls sustained a concussion and the Welsh center Jamie Roberts sustained a minor rib injury.

headline.main: Wales Tops Ireland in World Cup Tune-Up
headline.print_headline: Wales Tops Ireland in World Cup Tune-Up
